Trucking Profitability Dashboard

This project processes load info, cleans and validates it, stores it into a database and runs queries to analyze profitablity.

It is designed to track real world operations and support better load decisions.

Pipeliine

Raw Load Data (CSV)
        v
Data cleaning & validation 
        v
Metrics Calculation (rate/mile, profit/mile)
        v
Database Storage (SQLite)
        v
Query Analysis (profit by load type, totals etc)

Key Features
-Handles messy real world data (invalid inputs bad values)
-Calculates profitability metrics per load 
-Stores dta persistently into SQLite
-Runs queries to analyze performance by load type
-Designed to scale with real operational date

Note: Real business data in not included in this repo sample datasets are provided for demonstration purposes.